  npcName: William
  dialogueLines:
  - Hi Player, do you like the your grave ?
  - I'm only joking... kinda
  - So you want to know more about Opscuro huh ? Well it's not actually a evil place,
    though most people are scared to vist. We like it that way though so it doesn't
    bother us
  - Opscuro is a limbo of sorts, Spirits come here to rest while waiting to move
    on to the after life, this land is special and where able to interact with the
    terrain
  - Everyone here is peaceful and freindly, where just here waiting, well at least
    intill the fractures started happening
  - We have been affected the most from the fractures unfortuanly, well beside poor
    Septem. They where overtaken by corruption from Umbra Terra and fell. Atleast
    it gave Aether Terra the wake up call it needed, hense why your here
  - the fracture has cause some of the resedients to turn into ghouls that may attack
    you, they dont mean to i promise. Its simply that the spirts here all have used
    magic while alive our souls are intertwined with magic making the corruption
    seeping though relms affect everything here.
  - Goodluck saving our Island player, and dont mind the grave, its not your time
    yet.
